tu.be%2FPHe0bXAIuk0&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8IZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=cf1b9923\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PHe0bXAIuk0</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完唔明再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8a044f5c6df0682db650b1424664716f4bcabb","tid":1929172,"uid":128210,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T21:30:35.000Z","msg":"唔好理上面答你廢話的所謂高手，<br />\n緊急狀態要cash係手？<br />\n佢地都係係個事態發生咗，先勉強加個理由落去。（即股票跌咗價先講原因）<br />\n<br />\n假設再下一次美國總統再宣布緊急狀態，你一入市熊/沽空，然後股票係咁升，你又走上黎問理由。<br />\n佢地一樣可以作個理由咩野市場睇好後市呀之類的廢話答你。<br />\n<br />\n調轉講句，上面答到人咁叻的高手們，有無邊個入咗熊？有無倉睇下先呀？"},{"pid":"263d2a7fbd7076c1abf74346b6b6190c4f2c3f08","tid":1929172,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c250e1e005ee30ea3829b5d3b7196ea603b886f8","tid":1929172,"uid":143939,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T21:27:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PHe0bXAIuk0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPHe0bXAIuk0&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8IZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=cf1b9923\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PHe0bXAIuk0</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完唔明再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:13:41.000Z","msg":"消化唔哂，遲吓再睇"},{"pid":"702979036650daff4d7687a526881ca0c0e1106e","tid":1929172,"uid":46801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f90ac302e24558e5a82f8f28a17ab932ded797f","tid":1929172,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T20:02:16.000Z","msg":"如題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:14:42.000Z","msg":"因為大戶收割"},{"pid":"f48be750c45a03a2b428a33606d31c5c83086d60","tid":1929172,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"702979036650daff4d7687a526881ca0c0e1106e","tid":1929172,"uid":46801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f90ac302e24558e5a82f8f28a17ab932ded797f","tid":1929172,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20